---
title: Double Loaded Beef & Chorizo Jacket Potatoes with Cheddar Cheese & Garden Salad
description: Get a load of this: crisp and golden jacket potatoes, topped with a moreish beef mince and chorizo topping - which comes together in the pan with a good glug of tomato and our trusty garlic & herb seasoning. Serve with a simple salad to balance out the richness, and top it all off with mandatory shredded Cheddar.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/658251c834da163846f08ba0-cf3362a8.jpeg
